1. Adding HTML5 Audio
	1. You want to play native audio on your web page.

  	2. Add the audio element, with the src attribute referencing the location of your audio
	file and fallback content for older browsers:

	<audio src="audio.mp3" controls>
	</audio>

2. Adding HTML5 Video
	1. You want to play native video on your web page.
	2. Use the video element with the addition of a src attribute that references the location
of your video file:

	<video src="video.ogv" controls></video>

